ll|(all but 2)}}, gospel choir vocals {{small|(6)}}, lead vocals {{small|(9)}}\n*[[John Deacon]] \u2013 [[bass guitar]] {{small|(all tracks)}}, [[acoustic guitar]] {{small|(5)}}\n\n'''Additional personnel'''\n*[[Mike Stone (record producer)|Mike Stone]] \u2013 additional background vocals {{small|(8)}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Chart (1976\u201377)\n!Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Kent Music Report|Australian Kent Music Report Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"auchart\">{{Cite book|title=[[Kent Music Report|Australian Chart Book 1970\u20131992]]|last=Kent|first=David|authorlink=David Kent (historian)|publisher=Australian Chart Book|location=[[St Ives, New South Wales|St Ives, NSW]]|year=1993|isbn=0646119176}}</ref>\n|8\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Austrian Albums Chart<ref name=\"atchart\">{{cite web|title=austriancharts.at Queen \u2013 ''A Day at the Races''|work=Hung Medien|language=German|format=ASP|url=http://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=Queen&titel=A+Day+At+The+Races&cat=a|accessdate=4 March 2012}}</ref>\n|8\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[RPM (magazine)|Canadian RPM Albums Chart]]<ref>[http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=53gtrvbfj0gk7r9b4sd40dtvu0&q1=Queen+Day+At+Races&q2=Top+Albums%2FCDs&interval=30  Library and Archives Canada.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023102718/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=53gtrvbfj0gk7r9b4sd40dtvu0&q1=Queen+Day+At+Races&q2=Top+Albums%2FCDs&interval=30 |date=23 October 2012 }}  Retrieved 1 April 2012</ref>\n|4\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Megacharts|Dutch Mega Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"nlchart\">{{cite web|title=dutchcharts.nl Queen \u2013 ''A Day at the Races''|publisher=[[MegaCharts]]|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Queen&titel=A+Day+At+The+Races&cat=a|work=Hung Medien|language=Dutch|format=ASP|accessdate=1 April 2012}}</ref>\n|1\n|-\n|ali